snippet.textDisplay: I don't think I have felt happy and sad at the same time after hearing someone sing about their loved one, leaving em behind to embrace someone else :) :(. Coke Studio's take on this song comes as a breath of fresh air. I have been in love with Zeb Bangash's voice since the time I heard Bibi Sanam Janam many years back. The house band has made the song sound so good that it touches the senses ever so subtly but still leaves the listener overwhelmed with emotions. I hope more people listen to this song as it needs to be heard. Much power to Coke Studio and thumbs up for making such a gem of a song. Waiting for the next season.
